rows.label: qst200214_msg0001
rows.name:
Tuvari-san.
We heard from Jaruru, but[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200214_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, are you Jaruru's messengers?
Just perfect!

rows.label: qst200214_msg0003
rows.name:
I was in trouble because there wasn't
enough cargo. Could you guys
hurry and collect it?

rows.label: qst200214_msg0004
rows.name:
Uoooooh!
There is no way I would be
complicit in smuggling[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200214_msg0005
rows.name:
Wah! Wah!
Wait a second, Glen.

rows.label: qst200214_msg0006
rows.name:
What is it, Nia?
Right now, I am trying to make
this guy turn over a new leaf[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200214_msg0007
rows.name:
Glen, possibly Tuvari-san
might be unrelated to
the smuggling, you know?

rows.label: qst200214_msg0009
rows.name:
He said he'd mix it in with other cargo
right? Wouldn't it be better to
cooperate and find out the destination?

rows.label: qst200214_msg0011
rows.name:
Tuvari-san, leave the cargo collection
to us. But, could you
tell us what we should bring?

rows.label: qst200214_msg0012
rows.name:
Ah[ML:Dash ] What's missing is
2 Divine Beast Craniums and
5 Ancient Chalices.

rows.label: qst200214_msg0013
rows.name:
If you don't have them on hand,
I think you can get them by Salvaging,
so hurry up, please!

rows.label: qst200214_msg0014
rows.name:
Uoooooooh!! Somehow this
doesn't sit right with me!!

rows.label: qst200214_msg0015
rows.name:
Wh-what!?
Shouting out suddenly, what's wrong!?

rows.label: qst200214_msg0016
rows.name:
No, nothing!
Well then, we're off!
